      <title>债券交易员在数十年来最痛苦的宽松政策中将目光投向 2025 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/bond-traders-turn-to-2025-amid-most-agonizing-easing-in-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员很少会因为美联储的宽松周期而遭受如此大的损失。现在他们担心 2025 年会出现更多类似的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/bond-traders-turn-to-2025-amid-most-agonizing-easing-in-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 16:53:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国统计数据的侵蚀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-22/erosion-of-us-statistical-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国统计机构（包括发布月度就业报告的机构）面临财务压力，数据因此受到影响。从投资决策到地方发展资金，连锁反应影响到方方面面。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-22/erosion-of-us-statistical-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 14:01:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ChatGPT 推出两年后，交易员仍对人工智能“Roadkill”的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/ai-roadkill-fears-haunt-traders-two-years-after-chatgpt-debut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ChatGPT 的兴起引发了人们对人工智能将扰乱各类企业的担忧。聊天机器人发布两年后，其结果并没有像一些投资者预测的那样灾难性。但人们仍然很担心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/ai-roadkill-fears-haunt-traders-two-years-after-chatgpt-debut</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对于新兴市场来说，“明年运气会更好”难以令人信服</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/for-emerging-markets-better-luck-next-year-is-hard-to-believe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[专注于新兴市场的投资者在过去一年里没有什么值得庆祝的事情。或者更确切地说，在过去十年里也是如此。现在，唐纳德·特朗普的关税和贸易战的前景让一些人考虑彻底放弃这些投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/for-emerging-markets-better-luck-next-year-is-hard-to-believe</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
